title: Five-people Premade For The Mission 'Wait...Do What Now?'
body:
Heya, I'm in Team Cat and I am kind of in need for another four players in the game to just drop by into a game of Co-op vs A.I and do nothing for the rest of the game until the bots win just to get that sweet 2 BE.

Edit: The mission has been completed! Thanks, Parasyte!
